metadata.name: Crypto Yum #1
metadata.description:
Yusuke Toda was born in Tokyo in 1991. Graduated from Tama Art University, Department  
of Painting, majoring in oil painting.  
In her recent works, she expresses everything with the character "YUM" and  
She depicts a unique painting space centering on the black-and-white character named  
YUM.  
He is always happily playing alone in his paintings.  
Starting from existing portraits, he constructs his paintings by collaging images of clouds,  
animals, people, and plants.  
The paintings express how we, the viewers and the environment around us, willingly  
interact with each other and live in harmony.
